{"type": "article", "id": 22982, "title": "可旋转书架", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-29T07:08:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060717430928ZpIfeNPrbQckXB.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是由瑞典设家居品牌 Folkform 推出的一组可旋转的书架，像一个小的茶几或床头柜。他们使用了一种烧焦的木头，在可旋转的中轴上安装了一个立方体空间，像一个个小的窗口，每一面都不一样。 Folkform 的设计师认为人们会越来越需要实体书，相比于将书陈列在大的书架里，会更倾向挑选少量自己喜欢的书放在小的书架中。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607174308wtd3qAh9YgjSoGJH.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607174308RPy3zej568OWnrqs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.09615385\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607174308cHwYVhgqKmQCj2x7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}